I18N4Vaadin is a small add-on for Vaadin intented to make it easier to create localized applications.


BUILDING I18N4Vaadin
--------------------

In order to build I18N4Vaadin, you need Java SDK 6 and Ant 1.6 or later. The other dependencies
are included in this source code repository.

Fire up a command line and execute the following command:

  $ ant all
  
This will create both the add-on JAR and the WAR for the demo application in the build-directory.

USING I18N4Vaadin
-----------------

Please go to the following location for more information about using I18N4Vaadin:

  https://github.com/peholmst/I18N4Vaadin/wiki/Quick-Reference
  
